content: Basically it's great but several annoyances with help functions like "undo to last mistake" is often incorrectly showing (even after restart of game) or not showing when there definitely is a mistake. Also it sometimes gives me a hint penalty when I didn't choose to take a hint. All in all , it's a better playing experience to a avoid all help anyway, a and jusy play like you would on paper, but bugs are bugs.
